### ============================================================
###  S03-26 Web App — Contactos API
###  Base URL: http://localhost:3001
###  Usar con la extensión REST Client (VS Code)
### ============================================================

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3001

### [1] Crear un nuevo Contacto (Ficticio)
POST {{baseUrl}}/contacts
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "Ricardo",
  "lastName": "Pérez",
  "email": "ricardo.perez@example.com",
  "phone": "+5491122334455",
  "segmentType": "lead"
}

###

### [2] Obtener todos los Contactos
GET {{baseUrl}}/contacts
Accept: application/json

###

### [3] Obtener un Contacto por ID
@contactId = d290f1ee-6c54-4b01-90e6-d701748f0851
GET {{baseUrl}}/contacts/{{contactId}}
Accept: application/json

###

### [4] Actualizar datos de un Contacto
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/contacts/{{contactId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "lastName": "Pérez García",
  "segmentType": "client"
}

###

### [5] Eliminar un Contacto
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/contacts/{{contactId}}
